elect other select type of gift select method of payment then click the continue button 3 you should come to a page entitled annual gift designation under further designation select freeman spogli inst for int l studies under special instructions write please make my donation to the rural education action project reap fund enter the amount you wish to donate and answer the other questions then click the continue button 4 enter your personal information and click the continue button 5 enter your payment information and click continue your contribution will be sent to reap the university will issue you a receipt for your tax deductible contribution to reap we are very appreciative of your interest in reap and for your contribution toward our work on behalf of the reap team thank you stanford university all rights reserved 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints rss+ rss xml feeds
